ExecDesc.value: Apple Mac OS X ImageIO gifGetBandProc GIF Image Handling Integer Overflow (IPv6 Version)

EngDesc.value: There exists an integer overflow vulnerability in Apple Mac OS X ImageIO. The vulnerability is due to a boundary error in the "gifGetBandProc" function in ImageIO when decompressing a specially crafted GIF image file. Successful exploitation of this issue causes a denial of service condition and allows remote attackers to execute arbitrary code in the context of the application. (IPv6 Version)
